    <entry>
      <title>LaTeX学习笔记</title>
      <link href="2020/12/05/LaTeX%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/"/>
      <url>2020/12/05/LaTeX%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>我从2020年暑期开始接触<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>LaTeX</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\rm{\LaTeX}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.89883em;vertical-align:-0.2155em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord"><span class="mord text"><span class="mord textrm">L</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:-0.36em;"></span><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.68333em;"><span style="top:-2.904999em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord textrm sizing reset-size6 size3">A</span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:-0.15em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord textrm">T</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:-0.1667em;"></span><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.46782999999999997em;"><span style="top:-2.7845em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord textrm">E</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.2155em;"><span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:-0.125em;"></span><span class="mord textrm">X</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>，真心觉得它不愧为写作利器，特别对于理工科的学生以及教师工作人员来说，<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>LaTeX</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\rm{\LaTeX}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.89883em;vertical-align:-0.2155em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord"><span class="mord text"><span class="mord textrm">L</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:-0.36em;"></span><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.68333em;"><span style="top:-2.904999em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord textrm sizing reset-size6 size3">A</span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:-0.15em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord textrm">T</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:-0.1667em;"></span><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.46782999999999997em;"><span style="top:-2.7845em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord textrm">E</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.2155em;"><span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:-0.125em;"></span><span class="mord textrm">X</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>极大地加快了写作效率。对于刚入门的同志们我在这里强烈建议阅读文档:<a href="https://switwu.github.io/File/lshort-zh-cn.pdf">lshort</a>，想要阅读更多关于<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>LaTeX</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\mathrm{\LaTeX}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.89883em;vertical-align:-0.2155em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord text"><span class="mord textrm">L</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:-0.36em;"></span><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.68333em;"><span style="top:-2.904999em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord textrm sizing reset-size6 size3">A</span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:-0.15em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord textrm">T</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:-0.1667em;"></span><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.46782999999999997em;"><span style="top:-2.7845em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord textrm">E</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.2155em;"><span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:-0.125em;"></span><span class="mord textrm">X</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>的教程，推荐在<a href="https://z-lib.org">zlibrary</a>上搜索下载，另外<a href="https://latexstudio.net">LaTeXstudio</a>是一个不错的<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>LaTeX</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\rm{\LaTeX}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.89883em;vertical-align:-0.2155em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord"><span class="mord text"><span class="mord textrm">L</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:-0.36em;"></span><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.68333em;"><span style="top:-2.904999em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord textrm sizing reset-size6 size3">A</span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:-0.15em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord textrm">T</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:-0.1667em;"></span><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.46782999999999997em;"><span style="top:-2.7845em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord textrm">E</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.2155em;"><span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:-0.125em;"></span><span class="mord textrm">X</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>学习网站。</p><h1 id="latex须知"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#latex须知"></a> LaTeX须知</h1><h2 id="概述"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#概述"></a> 概述</h2><h3 id="tex"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#tex"></a> TeX</h3><p><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>TeX</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\TeX</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.89883em;vertical-align:-0.2155em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord textrm">T</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:-0.1667em;"></span><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.46782999999999997em;"><span style="top:-2.7845em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord textrm">E</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.2155em;"><span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:-0.125em;"></span><span class="mord textrm">X</span></span></span></span></span>是高德纳 (Donald E.Knuth) 开发的、以排版文字和数学公式为目的的一个计算机软件。高德纳从 1977 年开始开发 TEX ，以发掘当时开始用于出版工业的数字印刷设备的潜力。正在编写著作《计算机程序设计艺术》的高德纳，意图扭转排版质量每况愈下的状况，以免影响他的出书。我们现在使用的<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>TeX</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\TeX</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.89883em;vertical-align:-0.2155em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord textrm">T</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:-0.1667em;"></span><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.46782999999999997em;"><span style="top:-2.7845em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord textrm">E</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.2155em;"><span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:-0.125em;"></span><span class="mord textrm">X</span></span></span></span></span>排版引擎发布于1982年，在 1989 年又稍加改进以更好地支持8-bit 字符和多语言排版。<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>TeX</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\TeX</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.89883em;vertical-align:-0.2155em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord textrm">T</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:-0.1667em;"></span><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.46782999999999997em;"><span style="top:-2.7845em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord textrm">E</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.2155em;"><span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:-0.125em;"></span><span class="mord textrm">X</span></span></span></span></span>以其卓越的稳定性、跨平台、几乎没有Bug 而著称。<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>TeX</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\TeX</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.89883em;vertical-align:-0.2155em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord textrm">T</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:-0.1667em;"></span><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.46782999999999997em;"><span style="top:-2.7845em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord textrm">E</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.2155em;"><span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:-0.125em;"></span><span class="mord textrm">X</span></span></span></span></span>的版本<br />号不断趋近于π，当前为3.141592653。</p><h3 id="latex"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#latex"></a> LaTeX</h3><h3 id="latex的优缺点"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#latex的优缺点"></a> LaTeX的优缺点</h3><h2 id="latex命令和代码结构"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#latex命令和代码结构"></a> LaTeX命令和代码结构</h2><h2 id="用命令行操作latex"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#用命令行操作latex"></a> 用命令行操作LaTeX</h2><h2 id="宏包和文档类"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#宏包和文档类"></a> 宏包和文档类</h2><h2 id="latex用到的文件一览"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#latex用到的文件一览"></a> LaTeX用到的文件一览</h2><h2 id="文件的组织方式"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#文件的组织方式"></a> 文件的组织方式</h2><h1 id="用latex排版文字"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#用latex排版文字"></a> 用LaTeX排版文字</h1><h2 id="语言文字和编码"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#语言文字和编码"></a> 语言文字和编码</h2><h2 id="排版中文"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#排版中文"></a> 排版中文</h2><h2 id="latex中的字符"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#latex中的字符"></a> LaTeX中的字符</h2><h2 id="文字强调"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#文字强调"></a> 文字强调</h2><h2 id="断行和断页"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#断行和断页"></a> 断行和断页</h2><h1 id="文档元素"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#文档元素"></a> 文档元素</h1><h2 id="章节和目录"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#章节和目录"></a> 章节和目录</h2><h2 id="标题页"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#标题页"></a> 标题页</h2><h2 id="交叉引用"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#交叉引用"></a> 交叉引用</h2><h2 id="脚注"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#脚注"></a> 脚注</h2><h2 id="特殊环境"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#特殊环境"></a> 特殊环境</h2><h2 id="表格"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#表格"></a> 表格</h2><h2 id="图片"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#图片"></a> 图片</h2><h2 id="盒子"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#盒子"></a> 盒子</h2><h2 id="浮动体"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#浮动体"></a> 浮动体</h2><p>先下载发行版MikTeX或者TexLive，再选择一个编辑器如<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>TeX</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\rm{\TeX}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.89883em;vertical-align:-0.2155em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord"><span class="mord text"><span class="mord textrm">T</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:-0.1667em;"></span><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.46782999999999997em;"><span style="top:-2.7845em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord textrm">E</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.2155em;"><span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:-0.125em;"></span><span class="mord textrm">X</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>works或者<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>TeX</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\rm{\TeX}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.89883em;vertical-align:-0.2155em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord"><span class="mord text"><span class="mord textrm">T</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:-0.1667em;"></span><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.46782999999999997em;"><span style="top:-2.7845em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord textrm">E</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.2155em;"><span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:-0.125em;"></span><span class="mord textrm">X</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>studio，新建一个名为helloworld.tex的文档，输入以下代码并进行编译，你就可以得到一份名为helloworld的pdf文档。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">\documentclass&#123;article&#125;</span><br><span class="line">\begin&#123;document&#125;</span><br><span class="line">Hello world!</span><br><span class="line">\end&#123;document&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><a id="more"></a><h2 id="编辑器的选择"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#编辑器的选择"></a> 编辑器的选择</h2><p>主流的编辑器有WinEdt,<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>TeX</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\rm{\TeX}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.89883em;vertical-align:-0.2155em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord"><span class="mord text"><span class="mord textrm">T</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:-0.1667em;"></span><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.46782999999999997em;"><span style="top:-2.7845em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord textrm">E</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.2155em;"><span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:-0.125em;"></span><span class="mord textrm">X</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>studio,<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>TeX</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\rm{\TeX}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.89883em;vertical-align:-0.2155em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord"><span class="mord text"><span class="mord textrm">T</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:-0.1667em;"></span><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.46782999999999997em;"><span style="top:-2.7845em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord textrm">E</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.2155em;"><span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:-0.125em;"></span><span class="mord textrm">X</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>works等，也可以使用文本编辑器VScode(添加<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>LaTeX</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\rm{\LaTeX}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.89883em;vertical-align:-0.2155em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord"><span class="mord text"><span class="mord textrm">L</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:-0.36em;"></span><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.68333em;"><span style="top:-2.904999em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord textrm sizing reset-size6 size3">A</span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:-0.15em;"></span><span class="mord text"><sp